description: Palate Party Gourmet Food Truck is owned and operated by Food Network’s Judge Chef Robyn Almodovar, who was also a Top Finalist on FOX’S Hell’s Kitchen Season 10.  Chef Robyn emphasizes on bold and vibrant flavors only using the freshest ingredients possible.  While always focusing on Farm to Table and Sustainable Seafood.  Stop by and let us give you “A Party in Your Mouth” or let us cater your next gathering!
name: Palate Party Gourmet Food Truck
